@section web_script 动态服务器Dynamic Server

一个动态服务器，其实并不比静态文件服务器复杂更多：
As a dynamic server, it will not be more comprehensible than the static server above:
@code
var http = require('http');

var svr = new http.Server(80, function(r){
  r.response.write('Hello, World!');
});
svr.run();
@endcode

这里只是一个简单的文本响应，构建更复杂的动态服务器需要进一步修改。
The code just responses with simple text of  “Hello, World!” for example. Of course, it needs further modification for building a more comprehensible dynamic server.

@section web_both 动静合一Both static and dynamic supoort
当网站规模不大的时候，我们通常需要在同一台服务器上同时支持静态文件和动态请求：
When the website is small-scale, we commonly just need a server, supporting both static file and dynamic request.
